1. Edit code in this repo
2. **Commit and push to `main`**
3. GitHub Actions deploys to the droplet (~5–10 min)
4. Verify at http://178.128.161.215/

**Never** mark complete after only local changes.

## Deploy

```bash
git push origin main
```

Or user runs **`Deploy to Website.command`**.

